-- Johnston Press Creditors May Secure Right to Stake, Times Says
-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n
-- 2012-04-01T09:35:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-01/johnston-press-creditors-may-secure-right-to-stake-times-says.html
Johnston Press Plc (JPR) ’s creditors may
secure the right to acquire a stake in the newspaper publisher
as they negotiate its refinancing, the  Sunday Times reported ,
without saying how it obtained the information.  The company’s creditors include  Lloyds Banking Group Plc (LLOY) 
and  Royal Bank of Scotland Group Plc (RBS) , the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
